" contribuir al seguimiento y examen generales del Foro Político de Alto "
"Nivel sobre el Desarrollo Sostenible."

#: ../../SO1.md:1298
msgid ""
"Knowing the extent and location of degraded land is instrumental to "
"achieving land degradation neutrality (LDN) at national level and "
"supporting Parties in setting national voluntary targets."
